{{Lunisolar October}} '''October 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=Kannazuki|1=Kannazuki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}} then this is the last day of the month. Otherwise if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大}} then it is the second last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Events ==
* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1720|ja|1720|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} が『{{ill|Dai-Nihon-shi|ja|大日本史|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 』250巻を幕府へ献上
