== Deaths == * {{ill|Annin|ja|安永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 8th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1779|ja|1779|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 6|ja|12月6日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Emperor Go-Taien|ja|後桃園天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 、118代{{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1758|ja|1758|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ）
