{{Lunisolar October|qq=}} 
'''October 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|October (Lunisolar)|ja|10月 (旧暦)|lt=October (Kannazuki)|1=Kannazuki|2=ja|3=10月 (旧暦)|1=Kannazuki|qq=|12=draft}}  the 10th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小|qq=}}  then this is the last day of the month. Otherwise if the month is {{Nihongo|Big|大|qq=}}  then it is the second last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}}  day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}} . 

== Events ==

* {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ([[Gregorian calendar]]   {{ill|1720|ja|1720|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|November 28|ja|11月28日|qq=|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|Mito Domain|qq=|12=draft}} が『{{ill|Dai-Nihon-shi|ja|大日本史|qq=|12=draft}} 』250巻を幕府へ献上

== Births ==
* {{ill|Bunka (era)|ja|文化 (元号)|lt=Bunka|lt_ja=文化|qq=|12=draft}} 12nd year ([[Gregorian calendar]]   {{ill|1815|ja|1815|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|November 29|ja|11月29日|qq=|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Ii Naosuke|ja|井伊直弼|qq=|12=draft}} 、Tokugawa shogunate{{ill|Tairō|ja|大老|qq=|12=draft}} （+ {{ill|1860|ja|1860|qq=|12=draft}} ）

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Annin|ja|安永|qq=|12=draft}} 8th year ([[Gregorian calendar]]   {{ill|1779|ja|1779|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 6|ja|12月6日|qq=|12=draft}} ） - {{ill|Emperor Go-Taien|ja|後桃園天皇|qq=|12=draft}} 、118代{{ill|Emperor|ja|天皇|qq=|12=draft}} （* {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|12=draft}} ）

